OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FThe legacy of the most pioneering team
OL,7,Fin the history of women's football is
OL,8,Fset to be formally recognised at next
OL,9,Fmonth's Women's Football Awards.
OL,11,FThe Manchester Corinthians Ladies FC
OL,12,Fwas founded in 1949, paving the way
OL,13,Ffor the women's game today.
OL,15,FThe club rose to prominence during a
OL,16,Ftime when women's football in England
OL,17,Ffaced severe restrictions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
