OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777486270
OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FIn the wake of the Football
OL,7,FAssociation's 1921 ban, which
OL,8,Fprohibited women from playing on
OL,9,Faffiliated grounds, the Manchester
OL,10,FCorinthians overcame significant
OL,11,Finstitutional and cultural barriers to
OL,12,Fbuild a legacy of remarkable
OL,13,Fachievement.
OL,15,FTheir success, which extended far
OL,16,Fbeyond the UK, is now set to be
OL,17,Frecognised at a national industry
OL,18,Fawards ceremony.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
