PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777486270
OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FThe Women's Football Awards will
OL,7,Fformally recognise the Manchester
OL,8,FCorinthians as being pivotal in
OL,9,Fshaping women's football now.
OL,11,FDespite their achievements, the
OL,12,FCorinthians' story faded from public
OL,13,Frecognition for many years.
OL,15,FNow, as women's football continues its
OL,16,Frapid growth, their contribution is
OL,17,Fbeing rightfully acknowledged.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
