CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777486270
OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FThe award will be accepted by
OL,7,Fsurviving members of the squad, whose
OL,8,Ffirst-hand accounts have recently been
OL,9,Fcaptured in a feature-length
OL,10,Fdocumentary chronicling their journey.
OL,12,FThis recognition at the Women's
OL,13,FFootball Awards not only honours the
OL,14,Flegacy of Manchester Corinthians
OL,15,FLadies FC but also celebrates their
OL,16,Flasting impact on the development of
OL,17,Fthe women's game.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
