OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777486270
OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FJamie Carragher, who is co-hosting the
OL,7,FWomen's Football Awards with Gabby
OL,8,FLogan, said: "The Women's Football
OL,9,FAwards will be celebrating a group of
OL,10,Ffearless pioneers who refused to
OL,11,Faccept the limits placed upon them.
OL,13,F"The Manchester Corinthians didn't
OL,14,Fjust play football - they changed it
OL,15,Fforever. Their legacy is present in
OL,16,Fevery girl and woman who plays
OL,17,Ffootball today."
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@AOUyD@PO]
