OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FFormer Manchester City, Barcelona and
OL,7,FEngland footballer Toni Duggan, who is
OL,8,Fan ambassador for the Women's Football
OL,9,FAwards, asdded: "As an England women
OL,10,Fnational football team player, you
OL,11,Fknow you're part of something bigger.
OL,13,FBut this wouldn't have been possible
OL,14,Ffor me or any of my former teammates
OL,15,Fwithout the likes of Manchester
OL,16,FCorinthians.
OL,26,@qD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
