PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1777486270
OL,3,CManchester Corinthians Ladies FC to be
OL,4,Chonoured at football awards
OL,6,FThey are the reason that we are here
OL,7,Ftoday. Their courage and love for the
OL,8,Fbeautiful game has paved the way for
OL,9,Fgenerations of players like me - it is
OL,10,Fan honour to see their story
OL,11,Fcelebrated."
OL,13,FThe Women's Football Awards was
OL,14,Flaunched in 2023 and is Europe's first
OL,15,Fmajor awards event dedicated solely to
OL,16,Fcelebrating achievement across the
OL,17,Fwomen's game.
OL,26,@sD@LO]
